  • com.mr.http使用的com.mr.http中的类 
    类和说明
    MR_Cache
    An interface for a cache keyed by a String with a byte array as data.
    MR_Cache.Entry
    Data and metadata for an entry returned by the cache.
    MR_Network
    An interface for performing requests.
    MR_NetworkResponse
    Data and headers returned from MR_Network#performRequest(Request).
    MR_Request
    Base class for all network requests.
    MR_Request.Priority
    Priority values.
    MR_RequestQueue
    A request dispatch queue with a thread pool of dispatchers.
    MR_RequestQueue.RequestFilter
    A simple predicate or filter interface for Requests, for use by MR_RequestQueue.cancelAll(RequestFilter).
    MR_Response
    Encapsulates a parsed response for delivery.
    MR_Response.ErrorListener
    Callback interface for delivering error responses.
    MR_ResponseDelivery 
    MR_RetryPolicy
    Retry policy for a request.
